   Ge, Jin; Lai, Jennifer C., Univ Calif San Francisco, Dept Med, Div Gastroenterol \& Hepatol, San Francisco, CA USA.
   Sun, Steve; Owens, Joseph; Galvez, Victor; Gologorskaya, Oksana; Lai, Ki, Univ Calif San Francisco, UCSF Hlth Informat Technol, San Francisco, CA USA.
   Gologorskaya, Oksana, Univ Calif San Francisco, Bakar Computat Hlth Sci Inst, San Francisco, CA USA.
   Pletcher, Mark J., Univ Calif San Francisco, Dept Epidemiol \& Biostat, San Francisco, CA USA.
   Ge, Jin, 513 Parnassus Ave,S-357, San Francisco, CA 94143 USA.},
